imdb.plot outline: The definitive film series on luxury real estate, architecture, design and living the good life in Southern California. Inside each episode, we will illuminate what's trending in the Southern California shelter community, with a rotating lineup of resource-rich real estate lifestyle topics, such as "LA's Top Markets to Invest in 2016, LA Rams and LA Real Estate, Kitchens We Love, What you get for $10,000,000 in LA, Design Stars, and much more!"
